  <brief_title>The Outcomes of Seamless ADL Training Between Occupational Therapist and Nurse in Stroke Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Outcomes of Seamless ADL Training Between Occupational Therapist and Nurse in Stroke Patients</official_title>
