  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Ability of dressing and bathing</measure>
    <time_frame>6 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>The ability of dressing and bathing measured by PMR Siriraj dressing and bathing scale. Total score is 40 points , Patients were evaluated before and after training. If score increased 0-24 % means ability increase 0 level, 25-49 % means ability increase 1 level, 50-74 % means ability increase 2 level, 75-99 % means ability increase 3 level, and 100 % means ability increase 4 level.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
